description: The video shows a bathroom door from the hallway, with a date and time stamp in the top left corner. The camera is positioned to the left of the bathroom door. Through the partially open bathroom door, a tiled bathroom can be seen with a light on and a shower curtain visible. There is a picture frame on the wall to the left of the bathroom door and other objects on a table, but they are blurry. A small figurine or statue is in the foreground of the video, positioned on a surface. At the end of the clip, the sound of a door creaking open can be heard.

The video shows a security camera footage of an apartment entryway. A man is standing inside the entryway looking out of the door. The man is wearing a black shirt and a black baseball cap with the New York Yankees logo in orange. He is looking at something outside the door but it is not visible in the frame. The apartment is very minimally decorated. It has a white door, white walls, and a large black and white picture hanging on the wall. There is a wooden chair on the right side of the picture. A white shelf with some items and hangers with clothes on it is visible in the left part of the footage. There is also a small, light blue, wall-mounted device.  The footage is captured by a wide-angle lens, which makes the room appear distorted.  The video is timestamped 05/28/2024 at 15:03:12.

The video shows a man sitting in a chair in a room with a fireplace and a large TV. The man is facing the TV, watching a movie with a woman in it. The TV is on the wall behind the fireplace. There is a small table in front of the man with a pair of sunglasses on it. The man is wearing a blue shirt and casual pants. The room is well lit. There is a kitchen to the left of the man. There is a white closed door and a small plant on a shelf behind the man. The camera is pointed at the man from behind, and the video is slightly shaky.The man is watching a movie on the TV, but he doesn't seem to be very engaged. He is just sitting in the chair and staring at the TV. The man is not making any sounds, and the only sounds that can be heard are those from the TV and the birds chirping outside. The man is just watching the movie, and there is no interaction with anyone or anything else in the room.

The video is a black and white night time recording of a parking lot. It appears to be a security camera and is focused on a car that is parked in the lot in front of a closed garage.  The date and time are displayed in the top left corner of the video.  At about the 24 second mark, a loud "beep" sound is heard.
Error during upload/processing

The video is a security camera footage of a living room. A person in black pants and a black t-shirt is standing in front of a large window and they are trying to get something outside. There are two grey couches in front of the person. The living room has a blue and white rug with a geometric pattern and the walls are light brown. The person is bending down and appears to be trying to grab something with their left hand.

The video is a security camera shot of a residential street.  It is a sunny day and there are trees and houses visible in the background. The camera is positioned on the front lawn of a house and is pointed towards the street. The frame shows a blue recycling bin and a white car parked on the lawn in the bottom left corner. In the top right corner, the rear end of a black SUV is visible. In the center of the video, a small roundabout is visible.  A few cars can be seen driving in the roundabout. The date and time stamp 2024-05-28 11:26:57 are visible in the top left corner.  A loud "pee" sound is heard at the end of the video.

The video is a black and white security camera recording of a living room. It shows a ceiling fan with a light in the middle of the room, a dining table with a chair, and a large black leather recliner. The kitchen is visible in the background. The camera records a variety of noises, including a dog barking and a cat meowing, for approximately 42 seconds.

The video shows a family in their living room. There is a man sitting on the couch, while a little girl is standing near him and looking at something. Two women are sitting in front of the computer, and a little girl is sitting on the floor, playing with some toys. Another little girl is in the foreground, playing with a pink suitcase. The room is cluttered with toys and other items. The time and date are visible on the top left corner of the screen. There is a lot of talking and playing going on in the room. The women are talking to each other, and the little girls are playing with the toys. The man is not visible, but it sounds like he is talking to someone off-camera.The video appears to be from a security camera, but it is unclear why it was being recorded. It could be for security purposes or to monitor the children. At one point, a little girl asks, "Mommy, can I have some toys?" The woman replies, "You can have some toys. Come on, be nice." The video ends with a little girl saying, "Look at that!"

The video shows a black SUV driving down a residential street. It's a sunny day, and the street is lined with houses and parked cars. There are trees and bushes along the sidewalk, and the grass is green.  The camera is positioned on the front porch of a house, and the SUV is driving towards the camera. The car is moving slowly, and it is possible that it is looking for a specific address.  The timestamp in the upper left corner of the video indicates the date and time the video was recorded.

The video shows a close-up of a brick wall in black and white. The camera is stationary and the only movement is a shadow that appears and then disappears. It is not clear what is causing the shadow, or if it is even a shadow. There is no sound in the video.

The video shows a white pickup truck from an overhead perspective. The truck is parked in a parking lot. The hood of the truck has a black air scoop. A person approaches the truck and reaches into the hood. The person opens the hood and does something inside. Then the person closes the hood and walks away.

The video shows a black and white night vision camera shot from inside a home, looking out through a chain link fence. There is a car parked behind the fence, and a small tree can be seen to the right of the car. There is a bird bath on the ground near the tree. A tree with many branches is seen in the center of the shot. There is a paved area beyond the tree with more trees in the background. There is a tire on the ground to the right. The video shows a bird in the yard near the car. The bird is moving around and is making noises.

The video shows a car parked at night. The car is silver and appears to be a sedan. The car is parked on a paved lot that has a yellow painted line along the edge. The pavement is cracked and has some light vegetation growing through it. There are some bushes and grass on the edge of the pavement. The video is from a surveillance camera and the timestamp indicates that it was recorded on May 28, 2024, at 6:00:44. The video is static and only shows the car and the surrounding area. Near the end of the video, a loud buzzing noise is heard, like an insect.

The video shows a backyard porch at night.  The porch is lit by a single overhead light.  There is a white railing and a wooden panel on the back wall.  On the porch are a white plastic chair, a black chair with the words "Wildcats," "Highland Century Club," a bucket, and several other items. There is a potted plant with pink flowers on the railing.  The camera is mounted above and behind the railing. At 0:26, the sound of birds chirping can be heard.

The video is a still shot of a room inside a recreational vehicle or camper. The camera is mounted on the wall and is pointing towards the front of the vehicle. The shot shows the front door, a window with a curtain, and a table with a red fan on it. The fan is turned on and blowing air. There is also a couch to the right of the table. There are stairs in the background.

The video is a security camera recording from a kitchen. The date and time stamp is visible in the top left corner, showing May 28th, 2024 at 04:18. The camera angle is wide and looks over the kitchen counter and stove. The video shows a woman, with her back to the camera, wearing a grey hoodie and glasses, working at the counter. She is taking out a blue and white plastic container from the cabinet to the right of the stove. The counter is messy with several items, including a water bottle, a container labeled "kami," a wooden spoon and a blender. The stove has a large pot and a pan on it. The counter to the right of the camera has several items on it, including a microwave, a toaster oven, and a blue and white container. The woman continues to work at the counter, picking up items and putting them away in cabinets.

The video is a black and white night-time recording of a parked car in a driveway. A small tree with no leaves is in the background to the left of the car. There is a streetlight on the right side of the frame illuminating the car and part of the driveway. The date and time are displayed in the upper left corner of the frame. There is a light sound of a car beep in the background at 0:23.

The video is a security camera recording of a living room. A woman is walking in from the right. She is wearing a blue and yellow dress and carrying a piece of paper. She walks toward the left side of the room and out of the camera’s view. The living room has a brown couch, a piano, a coffee table, and a flat-screen television. The floor is hardwood and there are two red rugs. The video is cut off before she leaves the room. A male voice can be heard in the background saying, “the scammer would have had his money. I don’t know. Not. There’s no. There’s no money taken out of my account for that. There’s no transaction.” The video is likely from a home security camera and the woman is talking on the phone. The male voice is likely a family member who is concerned about the woman being scammed.

The video is taken from a security camera at night. It shows a gravel driveway and some greenery in the background. The image is black and white and the camera is angled slightly downward. There are a few sounds of birds chirping. At 0:24, a high-pitched, repetitive sound starts.

The video is a close-up shot of a woman's legs and torso, presumably recorded by a security camera. She is standing in a kitchen and talking to someone off-screen, complaining about the way her fridge door is closing. The woman says, "You know, it's hard to get the refrigerator door to close. It's off the track. It's not like it's going to go all the way in." She also says that she can't close the door because it's not going to the edge, and she's going to have to lift it.

The video is a black and white recording from a security camera.  There is a mat in the foreground and a wooden door in the background.  The video is a recording of the front door of a home.  A person is speaking in the background.  You can hear them saying "I am going to take my shoes off" and "That's exactly what I am going to do" and "Call is the country of a dictator" and other parts of a conversation.

The video is a still shot from a security camera. It appears to be in a kitchen or dining room. A brown table with a shiny surface fills the frame with the camera's angle pointing slightly down at the table surface. There is a chair in the background, a white cabinet on the left, and a beige wall. On the table, there is a white bowl, a black electrical appliance that appears to be a coffee maker, and three partially visible bottles. The video is silent.

The video is a black and white security camera feed from a room. There is a table in the center of the frame with a few items on it, including a calculator, two bottles, and a piece of paper with some handwriting. There is a lamp in the upper left corner of the frame and an armchair in the lower left corner. There are two chairs in the background, one on each side of the frame. The video is 1 minute and 16 seconds long. There is no audio.

The video is a black and white recording from a security camera. It shows a room with a white door to the left and a partially open door to the right. The camera is positioned on a table or desk, facing the room. There are several items on the table in front of the camera, including a bottle of lotion and what appears to be a phone. To the left of the camera is a large, black object that is likely a TV. It appears to be a night recording with a faint glow from a light source outside the camera's range. The video begins with the sound of a single "peep" and then a series of peeping sounds. The peeping sounds continue for several seconds before the video ends.

This video appears to be taken from a home security camera.  The camera is mounted on a porch looking out onto a grassy lawn with a concrete walkway leading to the front door. A tall, thin plant is growing near the walkway, and there are some bushes and trees in the background. The camera captures a still image, with no motion. The date and time are displayed in the top left corner of the frame: 05/28/2024 14:44:15.

The video shows a close-up view of a red wooden deck with a beige trailer home behind it. The camera is mounted on the wall of the trailer home, and it is pointed at the deck. The video is filmed in a fisheye lens, so the perspective is distorted. The video is very blurry and the audio is just a few seconds of light wind blowing through the trees. The day is partly cloudy and there is a slight sheen on the deck from a recent rain. It appears to have just stopped raining, as you can see water droplets still clinging to the camera lens.

The video is a security camera recording of a backyard. It is a still image that shows a grassy area with a single, large tree to the left. The camera is positioned at an angle and the perspective is skewed. In the foreground there is a black pickup truck with a white trailer attached to the back. The trailer is facing the camera and a portion of the trailer hitch can be seen, as well as a portion of the left tire.  The date and time stamp shows the video was recorded on May 28, 2024 at 05:56:37.

The video shows a suburban street with a house on a slight incline. The video was taken from a camera positioned on the driveway. There are a few cars parked in the driveway, including a black pickup truck and a silver sedan. The front lawn is a mix of grass and dirt and has some clutter near the house. A fence separates the front yard from the road. The trees are mostly deciduous and some are losing leaves. The day is sunny and the sky is clear. The camera remains stationary throughout the video.

The video is a recording from a security camera. It's a wide-angle view that looks out from the porch of a house. There are lush green lawns in the foreground, with a sidewalk leading up to the porch. The camera is pointed towards a street. There is a blue car parked in the driveway and a grey car driving in the street. It's a cloudy day and raining, and the wind is blowing the palm trees in the foreground. The video is dated 1/2/2024 at 18:19, and the sound is a loud beep.

The video shows a still image of a driveway with three cars parked in it. The camera is pointed at the rear end of the three cars. The furthest car is driving away from the camera, and the two closest cars are stationary. The car in the center has a sticker on the back window with a hockey logo on it. The car closest to the camera is a black sedan. The far-right car is a black car that is leaving the driveway. The video is taken from a security camera and the time stamp in the top left corner shows May 28, 2024 at 6:42:52 PM.

The video shows a living room with a ceiling fan, a black leather couch, a picture on the wall, a floor lamp, and a plant on the left side of the screen. There is a table in the foreground of the video and a white door in the background. The sun is shining through a window in the background, and a person is lying on the couch. The video is shot from a low angle, as if the camera is on a table, and appears to be shot with a home security camera. The video ends with a loud buzzing sound.

The video shows a security camera view of a self-storage facility. A green SUV pulls into the covered area at the start of the video. The SUV then backs up into a parking space, before driving away.  The camera's view is under a roof overhang, with a concrete floor and asphalt driveway. There are rows of storage units to the left of the camera, and a large, white building with windows on the right. A couple of air conditioning units, red pipes, and white poles are visible on the exterior of the building.

The video is a still shot of a living room, shot in black and white. The camera is positioned in the center of the room and is facing the far wall. The room is sparsely furnished with two white ceramic vases on the table in the foreground, a coffee table with a glass top and a couch against the far wall. In the background, to the left, there is a TV on a black stand with a chair in front of it. A dining table and chairs are visible in the far left corner of the video. The only sound present in the video is an undecipherable humming sound, likely made by a refrigerator in the kitchen that is out of view.

The video is in black and white and shows a small fish swimming in the water. The fish is swimming towards the left side of the screen. The water is dark and the fish is only faintly visible. In the top left corner of the screen, the date and time are displayed: 05/28/2024 00:27. There is a small logo in the bottom left corner that says "kami".  There is a faint "p" sound.

The video shows a backyard patio with a wooden deck. There is a large grey couch with pillows on it, a small coffee table, and a set of chairs and a table in the background. There is a small child's play structure, a hot tub, and a patio heater. The date and time is visible on the screen. There is a small bird perched on the railing of the deck. The bird begins to chirp.

This video is a security camera recording of a living room and kitchen.  A young man is eating cereal at the kitchen table, while someone else is talking. The sound of running water can be heard. The kitchen has light gray cabinets and a black refrigerator. The living room has a black couch with a zebra print throw, and a few pillows. A pink and white blanket is thrown on the floor near the couch. There is also a ceramic bowl, and a red toy lying on the floor in the living room.

The video is a still shot of a home office. The camera is facing the desk, which is cluttered with items, including a computer monitor, a keyboard, a mouse, a red phone cord, a few papers, and a dark red book. There is a grey office chair to the right of the desk, and a doorway to the left of the desk. There are several framed photos and pictures hanging on the wall to the left of the doorway, a backpack hanging on a hook on the wall, and a large bookcase to the right of the grey office chair. A brown-feathered hawk is perched on a lamp on the desk, facing toward the right of the frame. The video also shows a digital clock that indicates the date as 05/28/2024 and the time as 18:41:46. The video is a still shot and does not move.

The video is a surveillance footage from a security camera. It is a wide shot of a pink-colored backyard. The camera is pointed towards the left side of the yard, facing a pink wall. A pink motorcycle is parked in the yard, along with other items. The camera is positioned in a high place, looking down at the yard. The video is grainy and the colors are slightly distorted, which is typical of low-resolution surveillance cameras.

The video shows a black and white, low-light view of a storage room. The camera is pointing at a metal shelf unit filled with plastic storage bins. The bins are full of white and grey fabric. The video is shot with a wide-angle lens and a fisheye effect, so the edges of the image are curved.

The video shows a black and white security camera footage of a bare ground area with some trees on the side. There is a small white object in the middle of the ground. The time is 04:17:35, and it is a cloudy day. At 00:24, we see a set of headlights driving by in the background.

The video shows a room with a blue floor and large windows.  Through the windows, we can see a man walking with a black dog outside.  The room is cluttered with boxes, exercise equipment, and other miscellaneous items. The camera is stationary and fixed on the room, only showing a portion of the outdoor scene.  The man walks across the outdoor space, briefly out of frame, and then returns to walk across the space again.  The dog follows the man, sniffing the ground as it goes.  The video ends before the man and dog leave the frame.

The video shows a black and white security camera footage at night. It shows a view through a screen door. There is a bush in front of the screen door and some trees in the background.  There is some motion in the bushes and then a  sound like an animal panting can be heard (P-P-P-P).  The sound repeats many times, and it sounds like a dog. The video fades to black at the end.

The video starts with a close-up view of an American flag hanging upside down on a flagpole in a backyard. There are three light fixtures on the pole. The flag is waving gently in the breeze. The camera then moves down to show the rest of the backyard. There is a fenced-in area with green grass and trees. A white truck is driving down the street in the distance. The camera then pans up and to the right and the flag is still waving in the breeze. The light fixtures on the flagpole are reflecting the sun. The background is still a green lawn and trees.The video ends with a loud whistling sound.

The video shows a silver SUV parked in a driveway at night. The vehicle is facing the right of the screen. Behind the SUV is a white pickup truck which is pulling out of the driveway. There is a basketball hoop in the background. The camera has a slightly blurry view. The video is in black and white. A person walks past the white pickup truck near the start of the video.

The video shows a young girl lying in bed, hooked up to medical equipment.  A woman is standing over her, holding a small device and speaking in an unknown language. The woman is wearing a maroon shirt. The room is cluttered with various objects. The video is shot from a low angle, making it look like the camera is pointed up at the ceiling.

The video is a black and white recording of a porch in the evening. The camera is pointed at the entryway, and a porch railing is in the right side of the frame. A small rug is on the floor, and a brick wall with a light fixture is to the right of the door. A woman is standing at the edge of the screen holding a package, then walks into the frame and puts the package down on the floor. She looks back up and then bends down to pick up the package again, holding it up for the camera. She turns and walks away offscreen.

The video is a security camera recording from a high angle. The camera is pointed at a patch of grass, a small tree, and the edge of a paved driveway. There are some pieces of trash on the ground. A red car pulls up to the edge of the driveway, then reverses and drives away again. The audio is of birds chirping and leaves rustling in the wind.

The video shows a dark hallway with wooden stairs in the background. A door is partially open to the left of the stairs. The camera appears to be mounted in the doorway of a room on the right side of the hall. A voice can be heard, but only the sounds “ppppp” are clear. There are two light switches on the wall of the hallway, but neither of them are turned on. The hallway is lit by light coming from the partially open door.
